{"tid":951634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"四隻流浪狗「列隊守候醫院門口」！不吵不鬧等流浪漢主人出院回家","createTime":"2018-12-22T13:27:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-23T08:34:42.000Z","uid":212399,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"324c054ddb426bca335c6e3c3b0ae178f836b264","tid":951634,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T13:27:47.000Z","msg":"文／紅豆Q粉粿<br />\n動物對主人的忠誠有多動人？看完今天這則文章，各位就會明瞭。<br />\n一位名為C&eacute;sar的巴西男子，因沒有穩定收入，長年流落街頭。<br />\n有天，C&eacute;sar因重病在街頭昏厥，被好心人士送到醫院裡，過了一兩天，C&eacute;sar恢復精神、醒過來，但護理人員跑來對他說，「從你住院的那天開始，門口就有好幾隻流浪狗待著不走，是你的狗嗎？」C&eacute;sar趕緊跑到醫院大門查看，他感動地流下眼淚。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3762/3762523.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3762%2F3762523.jpg&h=fcd47da1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原來，C&eacute;sar雖然身無分文、貧窮潦倒，但是他很喜歡狗狗，平常，如果C&eacute;sar乞討數個小時後得到一些零錢，或是拿到好心人給予的食物，他都優先餵飽身邊遇見的流浪狗。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3762/3762522.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3762%2F3762522.jpg&h=307e7d3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n長期下來，不少流浪狗開始跟著他到處走，慢慢地把他當作主人般看待，不管是露宿街頭時，或是這次C&eacute;sar住院，這些狗狗都默默地聞著C&eacute;sar的氣味、跟在他身後，不願離開他。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3762/3762520.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3762%2F3762520.jpg&h=725b7a42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事後，照顧C&eacute;sar的護理人員拍下幾隻狗狗守候醫院門口的畫面，並PO上臉書，照片不僅感動眾人，也已被分享上萬次。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3762/3762519.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3762%2F3762519.jpg&h=54995dac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n寫到此，一方面希望C&eacute;sar早日康復，另一方面也想謝謝他，即便他窮苦，卻還是愛著動物&hellip;<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/40422\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fdalemon%2Fpost%2F40422&d=Hrp0fs57trArtuevVMsA6tibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=957025d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/40422</a>"},{"pid":"621ff3ba5886e1a2856547f837cfeb03cb16f44c","tid":951634,"uid":198583,"like":2,"dislike":25,"score":-23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T13:28:32.000Z","msg":"屌 佢就好 ..又有幾餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01ccef4a771e04bd78f068cc408604db28a91bb4","tid":951634,"uid":212399,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T13:29:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bec6c6e07d51ea385360773e878be3debc21df02","tid":951634,"uid":54337,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T14:34:47.000Z","msg":"愛護狗狗嘅外國乞衣，比起殺狗食狗嘅垃圾支那賤種生番，更似一個人"},{"pid":"66d3f3a24b3d98edc9f1294be8f08837b7f97d10","tid":951634,"uid":84267,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"bec6c6e07d51ea385360773e878be3debc21df02","tid":951634,"uid":54337,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T14:34:47.000Z","msg":"愛護狗狗嘅外國乞衣，比起殺狗食狗嘅垃圾支那賤種生番，更似一個人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T20:34:29.000Z","msg":"連登仔: 食狗又咩問題"},{"pid":"286eecfc80f5a919e3cfea9715a73af5c0db7557","tid":951634,"uid":52595,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T20:40:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fd2119f4542aa89baedeb4be53ccaa38d455c637","tid":951634,"uid":6111,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"bec6c6e07d51ea385360773e878be3debc21df02","tid":951634,"uid":54337,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T14:34:47.000Z","msg":"愛護狗狗嘅外國乞衣，比起殺狗食狗嘅垃圾支那賤種生番，更似一個人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T20:50:13.000Z","msg":"咩叫似？<br />\n根本佢就係一個人<br />\n支那賤畜永遠都只會係賤畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dfd9ba4e37167cf94ad66eb0f2a1891fdc691f0","tid":951634,"uid":207415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T21